name: RIP Amy
description: I had this strong urge to blast some Amy Winehouse the day this was taken. As I was listening to her record I started googling her and found out it was her birthday! ❤️ There’s is no such thing as a coincidence !! 🍷 BTW this my Genesis piece… I’ve been putting it off too long to list something because I wanted it to be perfect but at this rate it’ll never happen. So here ya go..
